\defgroup primateVision primateVision

This application simulates the primate dorsal stream.

\section intro_sec Description
Series of interdependent servers providing primate dorsal competencies:

- egocentric rectification

- egocentric spatiotemporal perception

- coordinated stereo fixation

- active-dynamic attention including dynamic inhibition of return, saliency, spatial bias.

\section dep_sec Dependencies
Assumes \ref icub_iCubInterface (headinstantiated) and \ref icub_dragonfly servers are runnin.

